Class ArticulatedLorry

java.lang.Object
Vehicle
Truck
ArticulatedLorry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Movable
public class ArticulatedLorry
extends Truck
A class that has the functionality of a transporter by having a Transporter object as a variable.
